# Architecture

This directory holds the current truth for `<repo-name>` documentation
structure.

## Belongs Here

- current repository documentation model
- current placement and ownership guidance
- current entry-point relationships

## Does Not Belong Here

- unresolved alternatives: `../Proposals/` when that subtree is present
- decision records and cutovers: `../Decisions/` and `../Migrations/` when
  those subtrees are present
- retired material: `../Archive/` when that subtree is present
- supporting reference material and examples: `../Reference/` when that
  subtree is present

## Typical Use

Use this subtree for the files that state what is true now.
